getDetailedAum.t.sol
├── when call is reentrant
│  └── it should revert
└── when call is not reentrant
   ├── it should account for all base-token positions
   ├── it should account for all positions, debt and non-debt
   └── it should return the caliber net AUM along with an array containing all encoded Caliber position IDs, their corresponding values, isDebt flags, and whether their accounting is stale
